    "body": "`cuda-gdb` needs `libncurses.so.5`, ( see https://docs.nvidia.com/cuda/cuda-gdb/index.html#common-issues-oss ). \r\nHence I first add a new variant to `ncurses` to build the ABI for version 5 and add this as runtime dependency for a 'dev' variant for `cuda`, which is useful for developing cuda apps.",
